<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verificarea metodei addProduct din ProductService. Clasa foloseste obiecte de tip mock pt Product, ProductValidator si Repository.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>- obiectele de tip ProductValidator, Repository si Product sunt mock</p>

<p>- ProductService este creat prin injectarea celor doua instante mock: ProductValidator si Repository</p>

<p>- Product este un produs valid</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
