<a name="toc_tc31039"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P237-101: Step2_Integration_SV_addProduct&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">tmir3641</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verificarea integrarii top-down depth-first dintre ProductService (S) si ProductValidator (V). Se testeaza comportamentul metodei addProduct folosind implementarile reale ale instantei Service si ale Validatorului, in timp ce Product (E) si Repository (R) sunt izolate prin obiecte de tip mock.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>- ProductValidator este un obiect real</p>

<p>- Repository este un obiect mock</p>

<p>- ProductService este creat prin injectarea validatorului real si al instantei Repository simulat</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.service.it.ProductServiceLevel1ValidatorIntDfTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.service.it.ProductServiceLevel1ValidatorIntDfTest#testAddValid_withRealValidator</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
